	tness class. Please bring a water bottle and an optional sweat towel. All 
	other equipment will be provided. \\nVital Sculpt HIIT meets every Tuesday
	 at 5:30 pm at the Phinney Center.\n\nhttps://www.phinneycenter.org/event/
	vital-sculpt-hiit-class-with-seattle-jazzercise/2026-03-24/\n\nFrom Phinne
